  "texts": [
    "As shown in Fig. 3, our initial query identified 6,290 records combining \"Artificial Intelligence\" and \"olfaction\" and 641 records combining \"Artificial Intelligence\" and \"gustation\" from Google Scholar since 2022.",
    "After removing duplicates, the remaining records were screened by title and abstract to exclude unrelated topics, such as studies not related to AI-driven sensory modeling, non-peer-reviewed sources, and those not focused on human or synthetic sensing systems.",
    "This multi-stage process narrowed down the dataset significantly.",
    "Studies were then assessed for eligibility based on inclusion criteria, which included relevance to AI-driven sensory modeling, availability of full text, and applicability to human or synthetic sensing systems.",
    "This process ultimately yielded 392 valid articles for further analysis."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}